OL,3,CAlmost a third of footballers impacted
OL,4,Cby online abuse, survey finds
OL,6,FData shared exclusively with ITV News
OL,7,Freveals the impact online abuse is
OL,8,Fhaving on professional footballers, as
OL,9,FITV News Sports Editor Steve Scott
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FWords by ITV News Senior Sports
OL,13,FProducer Joe Wardropper
OL,15,FAlmost a third of footballers say
OL,16,Ftheir mental health has been impacted
OL,17,Fby online abuse, according to the
OL,18,Fresults of a Professional Footballers
OL,19,FAssociation (PFA) survey shared
OL,20,Fexclusively with ITV News.
