OL,3,CAlmost a third of footballers impacted
OL,4,Cby online abuse, survey finds
OL,6,FThe anonymous questionnaire, answered
OL,7,Fby almost 1,600 players from 60 clubs
OL,8,Facross the Premier League, the English
OL,9,FFootball League (EFL) and the Women's
OL,10,FSuper League (WSL), found that more
OL,11,Fthan 450 footballers were
OL,12,Fpsychologically impacted by abusive
OL,13,Fcontent online last season.
OL,15,FBlackpool winger CJ Hamilton, who was
OL,16,Fracially abused on social media last
OL,17,Fmonth, told ITV News: "It doesn't
OL,18,Fsurprise me then that people are
OL,19,Fgetting affected by it."
