OL,6,FThe 30-year-old had scored both his
OL,7,Fteam's goals during a home match
OL,8,Fagainst Luton Town and was texting his
OL,9,Fmother after the game, when he checked
OL,10,Fhis social media account and
OL,11,Fdiscovered he had been sent two racist
OL,12,Femojis, one posted as a comment and
OL,13,Fthe other sent in a private message.
OL,15,F''It's something that plays on your
OL,16,Fmind because it's a mental thing you
OL,17,Fthink is going to happen every weekend
OL,18,F- like when you do well, or whatever,
OL,19,Fit's always in the back of your mind,"
OL,20,FHamilton added.
