OL,6,F"I've got a little boy now -
OL,7,Fobviously, he's of the same origins as
OL,8,Fme," he added.
OL,10,F''I don't want him to come (into) a
OL,11,Fworld where he gets it down the
OL,12,Fline...it's a bit sickening. So it is
OL,13,Fhard, but it's one of the things in
OL,14,Flife that we're trying to clamp down
OL,15,Fon at the moment.''
OL,17,FThe PFA is the footballers' union, and
OL,18,Frepresents more than 5,800 players in
OL,19,Fthe top flight of the men's and
OL,20,Fwomen's game, as well as the EFL and
OL,21,Facademies.
