OL,4,Cby online abuse, survey finds
OL,6,FDonervon Daniels, who plays for Oldham
OL,7,FFC and sits on the PFA's player board,
OL,8,Fsaid the survey revealed the "huge"
OL,9,Fnumber of players impacted by online
OL,10,Fabuse. He urged his fellow
OL,11,Fprofessionals to seek support if they
OL,12,Fwere targeted online.
OL,14,F"Most of the time, I think the players
OL,15,Fjust want to leave it alone," he said.
OL,16,F"They don't want to be abused and they
OL,17,Fdon't want to make a fuss about it."
