OL,6,FDaniels said that the idea that
OL,7,Ffootballers were less affected by
OL,8,Fnegative comments because they were
OL,9,Fhighly paid professionals "shouldn't
OL,10,Fenter the conversation".
OL,12,F"I think that perspective that you are
OL,13,Fdoing something you love, or you are
OL,14,Fearning a perceived amount of money,
OL,15,Fthat you are immune to the negative
OL,16,Fimpacts of a stranger telling you you
OL,17,Fare bad at your job or racially
OL,18,Fabusing you, that perspective is a non-
OL,19,Fstarter."
