OL,6,FFormer England goalkeeper David James
OL,7,Ftold ITV News that the scale of online
OL,8,Fabuse was "a very unfortunate
OL,9,Fsituation" but that sport could not be
OL,10,Fexpected to fix a societal problem.
OL,12,F"Unfortunately, I think there will
OL,13,Falways be people out there to make
OL,14,Fsure the person is being abused, it's
OL,15,Fa sad fact of life," he added at a
OL,16,FPremier League launch event before the
OL,17,Fstart of the 2024-2025 season.
OL,19,F"I think for the individuals involved
OL,20,Fwho are getting that abuse, I can't
OL,21,Fcondone any of it.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G8/14
